{"title":"蒙古谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因睡懒觉丢掉马匹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为吃骨髓损坏刀子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉汉讲的是自己实想的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩说的是亲眼看见的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天找不到黑夜找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天做不完冬天做。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有眼睛看别人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无镜子照自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人才出在贫寒家庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花开在死水泥中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对别人犹如深山猛虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对自己则像压蛋母鸡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬锅搭灶的人那有手不染黑的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出门单干的人那有不遇困难的。\t　王毓铭辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}